 Since the 2018 Forum on China-Africa Cooperation (FOCAC) Beijing Summit, China and Africa have been working closely on eight major initiatives, one of which is green development. From wildlife protection to environmental management, from meteorological watch to low-carbon city, from combat against desertification to joint scientific researches, China and Africa will face hand in hand our common environmental challenges and jointly build a greener future. Produced by Xinhua Global Serviceâ– 